flowchart TD
  Start([Start Session]) --> Landing[Open Landing Page /]
  Landing --> Questionnaire{Start Questionnaire?}
  Questionnaire -- Yes --> StartQ[Open /start and save draft answers]
  Questionnaire -- No --> AuthChoice
  StartQ --> AuthChoice{Choose Authentication Method}

  AuthChoice -- Sign Up Email --> Signup[POST /auth/signup]
  AuthChoice -- Sign In Email --> Signin[POST /auth/login]
  AuthChoice -- Continue with Google --> GoogleStart[GET /auth/google/start]

  GoogleStart --> GoogleCallback[GET /auth/google/callback]
  GoogleCallback --> GoogleExchange[GET /auth/google/exchange]

  Signup --> AuthOk{Auth Success?}
  Signin --> AuthOk
  GoogleExchange --> AuthOk

  AuthOk -- No --> AuthError[Show auth error and keep form values]
  AuthError --> AuthChoice
  AuthOk -- Yes --> PersistSession[Persist JWT session]

  PersistSession --> Bootstrap[Load /profiles/me via AuthBootstrap]
  Bootstrap --> BootstrapOk{Profile Bootstrap Success?}
  BootstrapOk -- No --> BootstrapRetry[Show retry state]
  BootstrapRetry --> Bootstrap
  BootstrapOk -- Yes --> GuardCheck{Onboarding Completed?}

  GuardCheck -- No --> Onboarding[Open /app/onboarding]
  Onboarding --> PhotoRule{At least one photo selected?}
  PhotoRule -- No --> PhotoError[Show photo required validation]
  PhotoError --> Onboarding
  PhotoRule -- Yes --> SaveOnboarding[POST /profiles/me and POST /preferences/me]
  SaveOnboarding --> OnboardingSaved{Save Success?}
  OnboardingSaved -- No --> OnboardingRetry[Keep form state and show API errors]
  OnboardingRetry --> Onboarding
  OnboardingSaved -- Yes --> Dashboard[Open /app dashboard]

  GuardCheck -- Yes --> Dashboard
  Dashboard --> Discover[Open /app/discover]
  Discover --> FeedLoad[GET /discovery/feed]
  FeedLoad --> FeedOk{Feed Load Success?}
  FeedOk -- No --> FeedRetry[Show retry action]
  FeedRetry --> FeedLoad
  FeedOk -- Yes --> SwipeChoice{Swipe Action}

  SwipeChoice -- Pass --> SwipePass[POST /discovery/swipe action=dislike]
  SwipePass --> Discover

  SwipeChoice -- Like --> SwipeLike[POST /discovery/swipe action=like]
  SwipeLike --> MatchResult{Mutual Match Created?}
  MatchResult -- No --> Discover
  MatchResult -- Yes --> Matches[Open /app/matches and GET /matches/me]

  Matches --> ChatOpen[Open /app/chat/:matchId and GET /chat/:matchId]
  ChatOpen --> ChatReady{Conversation Available?}
  ChatReady -- No --> ChatRetry[Show retry failed action]
  ChatRetry --> ChatOpen
  ChatReady -- Yes --> SendMessage[Send real-time message via socket]
  SendMessage --> ContinueChat{Continue chatting?}
  ContinueChat -- Yes --> SendMessage
  ContinueChat -- No --> End([End Session])

  Discover --> SessionCheck{Session Expired 401?}
  SessionCheck -- Yes --> SessionRecover[Redirect /login?reason=session-expired]
  SessionRecover --> LoginResume[Open login page and resume auth]
  LoginResume --> AuthChoice
  SessionCheck -- No --> SwipeChoice
